room_title: Escape room "The Mayan Temple" by Captured LV Escape Room in Bethlehem
room_description:
Hot on the trail of a renowned Mayan historian, Professor Rockford, you and your team of archaeologists stand at the entrance of the legendary Tikal Temple. This is the last known resting place of the relic called Calendar Cycles. Time is of the essence, you must locate the calendar and prevent the apocalypse!
WARNING: People with medical sensitivity to flashing light should not experience this attraction.
